# DAST Engine Implementation – Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A SaaS-ready Dynamic Application Security Testing (DAST) engine with **7 modular scanner modules**, a **SPA-aware Selenium crawler**, **async scan orchestration**, and an **aggregated Flask API**.

---

