## How to Use

Start the server:
```bash
cd backend
.\venv\Scripts\python app.py
```

Send a scan request:
```json
POST http://localhost:5000/api/scan
{
    "url": "https://target-site.com",
    "scans": ["sqli", "xss", "csrf", "auth", "ssl", "headers"],
    "depth": "standard"
}
```

Response includes: `url`, `score`, `grade`, `severity_counts`, `results[]`, `ai_analysis`, `crawl_info`.

Each vulnerability in `results[]` has: `name`, `severity`, `location`, `parameter`, `description`, `impact`, `recommendation`, `evidence`.
